ugp.org.javafx.animation

Class Interpolators

  • java.lang.Object
    • ugp.org.javafx.animation.Interpolators

  • public class Interpolators
extends java.lang.Object
    Rework of premade interpolators from Interpolator. These interpolators are based on cubicBezier(double, double, double, double) which is relative to cubic-bezier from html and more accurate version of Interpolator.SPLINE(double, double, double, double)!

    In html, this class would be called "transition-timing-functions". Here can see and make a your cubic-beziers.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    PETO

      • valueOf

        public static javafx.animation.Interpolator valueOf(java.lang.String name)
        Parameters:
        name - | Name of interpolator / transition timing function.
        Returns:
        Content of this utility class from string. Functions are "cubicbezier(double, double, double, double)", "steps(int, start|end)", general syntax is [name](args...)!
        If you mess something up the EASE will be returned and you will receive an error.
